{"tid":530744,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［非打飛機］深圳想超越香港仲差好遠","createTime":"2018-01-16T05:47:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-16T08:30:01.000Z","uid":95397,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a5200ede2a67eabbbbdbc361843afda23de93cf4","tid":530744,"uid":95397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T05:47:03.000Z","msg":"琴日陪老母去深圳<br />\n發現呢個城市都仲有好多問題<br />\n1.人民質素<br />\n班人可以做到理所當然地隨地拋垃圾同吐痰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個問題無2-3代人既教育都唔會改善到<br />\n<br />\n2.設施殘舊<br />\n羅湖個巴士站又焗又臭<br />\n好多巴士都好舊，連想望出窗睇景都覺得塊玻璃濛<br />\n深圳仲有好多路都熔熔爛爛（仲要有污糟既積水）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3.衛生惡劣<br />\n已唔敢去佢地既廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n諗到再講"},{"pid":"9c9ff91b6440d9ad29baff2ae83d4de2581b8447","tid":530744,"uid":95397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T05:49:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b0e3a00af365345f7044766410b2ac4ca59334d","tid":530744,"uid":53666,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T05:53:42.000Z","msg":"基本上成支那都係"},{"pid":"fc78aed459a684a23d1d7ae97bffb0c1717cc2cf","tid":530744,"uid":55511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T05:57:19.000Z","msg":"人地經濟起飛  理撚得你就街屙屎咩"},{"pid":"f91f7ff8a9cc5742c640fbb58a90091d9c960b11","tid":530744,"uid":26168,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T06:01:41.000Z","msg":"根撚本成日叫人上去睇吓人地幾撚進步嗰d 自己肯定未上過去<br />\n由始至終都係垃撚圾"},{"pid":"c258f349a78fc3386f9afa9f5a7baaab66c9a5eb","tid":530744,"uid":95397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T06:03:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根撚本成日叫人上去睇吓人地幾撚進步嗰d 自己肯定未上過去<br />\n由始至終都係垃撚圾</blockquote><br />\n我老母仲吹奏支那寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73b223600d02bf3b49e489ee00707c602b2e739c","tid":530744,"uid":95397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T06:04:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>基本上成支那都係</blockquote><br />\n堆人鍾意拎深圳黎比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我去完咪講下"},{"pid":"82fba14cccd8d8d2bdd327e6d3695d5eb2f8f6a9","tid":530744,"uid":13503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T06:04:25.000Z","msg":"街道地磚高低不平單車亂鳩拍，無單車徑電動車喺行人路橫沖直撞"},{"pid":"7facb18654e3183c26792036c59e7a310c583177","tid":530744,"uid":89530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T06:04:32.000Z","msg":"之前去過西安，成個城市質素都好過深圳，無論人定市容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n深圳好垃圾"},{"pid":"b006f7d8fcc17a4608a9d88028581a5ab3905319","tid":530744,"uid":59929,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T06:05:01.000Z","msg":"大陸既領先城市但係始終都係大陸標準既好(國際先進社會既垃圾)<br />\n雖然香港已經係中國城市 但始終香港既根基係以國際標準建設 (有慢慢進入大陸標準既勢)"},{"pid":"3db305b046c37c08dba5dc46be20cc57ff1ce38d","tid":530744,"uid":95397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T06:05:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前去過西安，成個城市質素都好過深圳，無論人定市容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n深圳好垃圾</blockquote><br />\n深圳多外省人？"},{"pid":"df62436429bf310bf9f159e89e71efc2c68f99ed","tid":530744,"uid":45613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T07:39:33.000Z","msg":"冇連登"},{"pid":"24e09b2e228b116cb8017201402c1e5a56c75503","tid":530744,"uid":115644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T07:41:03.000Z","msg":"都仲未追到香港，雖然香港呢家係渣"},{"pid":"cf72e35426d9b89b468e08cac9942a6084509164","tid":530744,"uid":165080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T07:45:58.000Z","msg":"香港人既質數愈黎愈差，已經同大陸唔差得多。<br />\n一日150個單程證，大批6A湧入，不斷同化港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42d7872837f796661569955fd28cfcadc93f9718","tid":530744,"uid":62532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T08: